<p>Now, here's the trick: if <code>$subscription-&gt;status == 'past_due'</code>, then it means that
the invoice <em>has</em> been created and we're having problems charging it. In this case,
set <code>$cancelAtPeriodEnd</code> to <code>false</code>:</p>
