</p>
<p>This converts that timestamp into a <code>\DateTime</code> object.</p>
<p>Now, if <code>$currentPeriodEnd &lt; new \DateTime('+1 hour')</code>, then this means that we're
probably in that window and should set <code>$cancelAtPeriodEnd = false</code>:</p>
