<p>Finally, we can use the <code>status</code> field to know whether or not the subscription has
truly been canceled, or if it's still active until the period end. In other words,
if <code>$stripeSubscription-&gt;status == 'canceled'</code>, then the subscription is done! Else,
we're canceling at period end and should just call <code>deactivate()</code>:</p>
