<p>To handle full cancelation, open up <code>Subscription</code> and add a new public function
called <code>cancel()</code>. Here, set <code>$this-&gt;endsAt</code> to right now, to guarantee that it will
look canceled, and <code>$this-&gt;billingPeriodEndsAt = null</code>:</p>
